snippet.title: T a k e Y o u r T i m e レースゲーム Trailer Updated
snippet.description:
We're on our way to Steam Greenlight, hoping to join it really soon!
You can actually find us on Steam Concepts and on the other following pages!

Join us in the race!

Steam Greenlight Concept: https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=741196869&searchtext=

Itch.io: https://spacebananagms.itch.io/takeyourtimeracinggame

Official website: http://www.spacebananastudio.com

Many thanks to all the guys who keep suggesting us improvements and ideas and, please, h a v e  f u n  w i t h  c l a s s.
